吉布森是一位兇猛的選手，他在場上很少微笑，而且常常投出{{le|近身球|brushback pitch}}以建立優勢並威嚇打者，這與他同時期的名人堂成員[[唐·德萊斯戴爾|唐·德萊斯戴爾]]風格類似<ref>[https://books.google.com/books?id=vzQDAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA38&lpg=PA38&dq=bob+gibson+baseball+digest&source=bl&ots=vAai44DXlL&sig=YziRJeqKKipMIqXBN2iEQo9P7_g&hl=en&ei=vVTMSvSPFcuttgeorNTiAQ&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=7#v=onepage&q=bob%20gibson%20baseball%20digest&f=false "Hall Of Famer Defends Inside Pitches To Batter"], by Art Spander, ''Baseball Digest'', November 1987, Vol. 46, No. 11, ISSN 0005-609X</ref>。即便如此，吉布森仍有著相當好的控球，生涯僅102次觸身球，比德萊斯戴爾的154次還要少<ref name=stats1/>。

吉布森即便是面對隊友也是粗魯無禮，像是當他搭配的捕手{{le|提姆·麥卡佛|Tim McCarver}}走上投手丘欲開會時，吉布森不僅忽略他說的話，還說到「你唯一要知道與投球有關的事就是球很難被打到<ref group="註腳">"The only thing you know about pitching is that it's hard to hit."</ref>。」<ref>[https://books.google.com/books?id=PorJ0P9XhcIC&pg=PA130&lpg=PA130&dq=bob+gibson+the+only+thing+you+know+about+pitching+is+that+it+is+hard+to+hit&source=bl&ots=rPhO9MoTs4&sig=6b7-WjtbZQeKL39JENogsPlPfpY&hl=en&sa=X&ei=yQE7Vfp8hMWiBOiugPgM&ved=0CEUQ6AEwBg#v=onepage&q=bob%20gibson%20the%20only%20thing%20you%20know%20about%20pitching%20is%20that%20it%20is%20hard%20to%20hit&f=false Tim McCarver's Baseball for Brain Surgeons and Other Fans: Understanding and Interpreting the Game So You Can Watch It Like a Pro (Google eBook)] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160603161109/https://books.google.com/books?id=PorJ0P9XhcIC&pg=PA130&lpg=PA130&dq=bob+gibson+the+only+thing+you+know+about+pitching+is+that+it+is+hard+to+hit&source=bl&ots=rPhO9MoTs4&sig=6b7-WjtbZQeKL39JENogsPlPfpY&hl=en&sa=X&ei=yQE7Vfp8hMWiBOiugPgM&ved=0CEUQ6AEwBg#v=onepage&q=bob%20gibson%20the%20only%20thing%20you%20know%20about%20pitching%20is%20that%20it%20is%20hard%20to%20hit&f=false |date=2016-06-03 }}, by Tim McCarver and Danny Peary, Random House Publishing Group, May 22, 2013</ref>

吉布森若無其事地將其威嚇性的名聲置之度外，儘管他曾說到他沒有刻意要表現出威嚇。在聖路易斯公共廣播電台的訪談中他曾打趣道，他投球時面目猙獰的唯一理由，是因為他沒有眼鏡去看清捕手的暗號所致<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.stlpublicradio.org/programs/slota/archivedetail.php?showid=3703|title=St. Louis Public Radio - St. Louis on the Air|website=Stlpublicradio.org|accessdate=2018-09-22|archive-date=2009-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090924144232/http://stlpublicradio.org/programs/slota/archivedetail.php?showid=3703}}</ref>。

==退休後生涯==
1975年賽季結束後，紅雀隊總經理{{le|賓·德文|Bing Devine}}曾在吉布森返回家鄉奧馬哈前，提供一份具體內容未定的工作給後者，但細節還待球隊官方高層批准<ref>[[#Gib94|Gibson and Wheeler 1994]]: 249–250</ref>。由於不確定未來生涯走向，吉布森拒絕這項提議，並在1975年休賽季時用了紅雀隊給他當做退休禮物的{{le|旅宿車|Motorhome}}到[[美國西部|美國西部]]四處旅遊。回到奧馬哈後，吉布森持續擔任當地銀行的董事會成員，並曾一度成為{{le|KOWH|KCRO}}廣播電台的主要投資者，還開了家名為「吉布森的精神與寄託（Gibson's Spirits and Sustenance）」的餐廳，有時會以老闆身分在裏頭一天工作12小時<ref>[[#Gib94|Gibson and Wheeler 1994]]: 257–259</ref>。

1981年，吉布森回到棒球場上，這年他接受了[[紐約大都會隊|紐約大都會隊]][[總教練_(棒球)|總教練]][[喬·托瑞|喬·托瑞]]的邀請，成為教練團的一員<ref>[[#Gib94|Gibson and Wheeler 1994]]: 257</ref>。托瑞給吉布森的職稱是「態度教練（attitude coach）」，這是大聯盟史上第一次有這樣的教練<ref>[[#Gib94|Gibson and Wheeler 1994]]: 262</ref>。1981年賽季結束後球隊解雇了托瑞和其教練團，因此托瑞在1982年轉任[[亞特蘭大勇士隊|亞特蘭大勇士隊]]總教練，並再次聘請吉布森作為{{le|投手教練|pitching coach}}<ref>[[#Gib94|Gibson and Wheeler 1994]]: 263–264</ref>。這年勇士隊是自1969年以來首度衝擊國聯冠軍頭銜，但最終在{{le|1982年國聯冠軍賽|1982 National League Championship Series}}中敗給了紅雀隊<ref>[[#Gib94|Gibson and Wheeler 1994]]: 264–267</ref>。吉布森和托瑞在勇士隊一直搭檔到1984年賽季結束<ref>[[#Gib94|Gibson and Wheeler 1994]]: 268–269</ref>。之後四年（1985年至1989年間），吉布森在廣播電台{{le|KMOX}}擔任紅雀隊棒球比賽賽前及賽後秀的主持<ref>[[#Gib94|Gibson and Wheeler 1994]]: 271–272</ref>。吉布森也曾於1990年擔任{{le|ESPN美國職棒大聯盟|ESPN Major League Baseball|ESPN}}棒球比賽的{{le|球評|color commentator}}，但隔年就因陪伴家人時間過少而拒絕繼續擔任<ref>[[#Gib94|Gibson and Wheeler 1994]]: 272</ref>。{{le|1995年聖路易紅雀隊球季|1995 St. Louis Cardinals season|1995年}}，吉布森再次以{{le|聖路易紅雀隊教練列表|List of St. Louis Cardinals coaches|投手教練}}的身分擔任托瑞教練團的一員，這是他繼20年前以球員身分退休後的再度回歸紅雀隊<ref name=retrobob/>。

== 個人生活 ==
吉布森有三個小孩，兩個是跟第一任妻子夏琳（Charline）所生，和第二任妻子溫蒂（Wendy）則育有另一個<ref>[[Bob_Gibson#Gib94|Gibson and Wheeler 1994]]: 258</ref>。

2019年7月，吉布森多年的經紀人迪克·茲茲曼（Dick Zitzmann）發表聲明到，吉布森在數個月前被診斷出[[胰臟癌|胰臟癌]]並開始化療<ref>{{cite web |author=Post-Dispatch store |url=https://www.stltoday.com/sports/baseball/professional/cardinal-beat/cards-hall-of-famer-gibson-being-treated-for-pancreatic-cancer/article_46a09769-7e70-5a86-9bc2-fea2d7748b64.html |title=Cards' Hall of Famer Gibson being treated for pancreatic cancer | Cardinal Beat |publisher=stltoday.com |date= |accessdate=2020-10-03 |archive-date=2019-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190714232543/https://www.stltoday.com/sports/baseball/professional/cardinal-beat/cards-hall-of-famer-gibson-being-treated-for-pancreatic-cancer/article_46a09769-7e70-5a86-9bc2-fea2d7748b64.html}}</ref>。2020年10月2日，在與胰腺癌奮鬥超過一年後，吉布森於[[安寧病房|安寧病房]]中逝世，享壽84歲<ref>{{cite web |last=Hummel |first=Rick |url=https://www.stltoday.com/sports/baseball/professional/cardinals-hall-of-famer-bob-gibson-dies-at-84-after-bout-with-cancer/article_90a0dff7-bee3-5a81-9eb0-91663f29fb4d.html |title=Cardinals Hall of Famer Bob Gibson dies at 84 after bout with cancer | St. Louis Cardinals |publisher=stltoday.com |date= |accessdate=2020-10-03 |archive-date=2020-10-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201003064715/https://www.stltoday.com/sports/baseball/professional/cardinals-hall-of-famer-bob-gibson-dies-at-84-after-bout-with-cancer/article_90a0dff7-bee3-5a81-9eb0-91663f29fb4d.html}}</ref>。

==榮譽==
[[File:CardsRetired45.PNG|thumb]]]]
1975年9月1日，[[聖路易紅雀隊|聖路易紅雀隊]]將吉布森的背號45退休<ref>{{cite web |author1=Por Jenifer Langosch |title=Cardinals' all-time retired numbers |url=https://www.mlb.com/news/cardinals-retired-numbers-c300073858 |website=mlb.com |accessdate=2020-12-08 |date=2019-03-11 |archive-date=2021-05-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210524092847/https://www.mlb.com/news/cardinals-retired-numbers-c300073858 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[1981年美國國家棒球名人堂票選|1981年]]，他被選為棒球名人堂成員<ref>{{cite web|url=http://mlb.mlb.com/stl/history/retired_numbers.jsp|title=Cardinals Retired Numbers|website=St. Louis Cardinals|accessdate=2018-09-22|archive-date=2018-09-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180922173451/http://mlb.mlb.com/stl/history/retired_numbers.jsp}}</ref>。1999年，吉布森在{{le|體育新聞|The Sporting News}}列出之最偉大的一百位棒球選手中名列31名，再被球迷選為[[美國職棒大聯盟世紀球隊|美國職棒大聯盟世紀球隊]]<ref>[[#Smi91|Smith 1998]]: 72</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://mlb.mlb.com/mlb/history/mlb_history_moreinfo.jsp|title=The All-Century Team|website=Major League Baseball|accessdate=2018-09-22|archive-date=2010-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100119065808/http://mlb.mlb.com/mlb/history/mlb_history_moreinfo.jsp}}</ref>。{{le|聖路易星光大道|St. Louis Walk of Fame}}上有屬於他的星星<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.stlouiswalkoffame.org/inductees/?view=achievement|title=St. Louis Walk of Fame Inductees|last=St. Louis Walk of Fame|website=Stlouiswalkoffame.org|accessdate=2013-04-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121031162946/http://www.stlouiswalkoffame.org/inductees/?view=achievement|archive-date=2012-10-31}}</ref>。{{le|哈里·韋伯|Harry Weber (sculptor)}}為吉布森所做的銅像坐落在[[布希體育場|布希體育場]]的前面，與其他紅雀隊名人代表的銅像一同做紀念<ref>{{cite web |title=The Sporting Statues Project_ Bob Gibson_ St Louis Cardinals, Busch Stadium, St Louis, MO |url=http://www.offbeat.group.shef.ac.uk/statues/STUS_Gibson_Bob_1.htm |website=The Sporting Statues Project |accessdate=2020-12-08 |archive-date=2021-02-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210219073452/http://www.offbeat.group.shef.ac.uk/statues/STUS_Gibson_Bob_1.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2013年，吉布森另外一座雕像在其家鄉[[奧馬哈_(內布拉斯加州)|奧馬哈]]的{{le|維爾納公園|Werner Park}}外揭幕<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.omaha.com/sports/bob-gibson-statue-unveiled-at-werner-park/article_f1bd6dbf-2963-547d-b7ea-f7b247fa7ad5.html|title=Bob Gibson statue unveiled at Werner Park|author=Rob White|website=Omaha.com|accessdate=2018-09-22|archive-date=2021-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211019191535/https://omaha.com/sports/bob-gibson-statue-unveiled-at-werner-park/article_f1bd6dbf-2963-547d-b7ea-f7b247fa7ad5.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://ballparkdigest.com/201304156199/minor-league-baseball/features/bob-gibson-statue-unveiled-at-werner-park|title=Bob Gibson statue unveiled at Werner Park|date=2013-04-15|website=Ballparkdigest.com|accessdate=2018-09-22|archive-date=2015-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150325195607/http://ballparkdigest.com/201304156199/minor-league-baseball/features/bob-gibson-statue-unveiled-at-werner-park}}</ref>。同樣位於奧馬哈的{{le|羅森布拉特體育館|Rosenblatt Stadium}}<ref group="註腳">吉布森家鄉以前在{{le|美國大學棒球世界大賽|College World Series}}中的主場</ref>，其北邊的一條街被命名為鮑勃·吉布森大道（Bob Gibson Boulevard）以示紀念<ref>{{cite web |author1=Fred W. Kiger |title=More Info on Bob Gibson |url=http://www.espn.com/classic/000726bobgibsonadd.html |website=ESPN.com |accessdate=2020-12-08 |archive-date=2021-02-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210219073515/http://www.espn.com/classic/000726bobgibsonadd.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author1=Sally Tippett Rains |title=Residents on a street in St. Louis have special memories of the day Bob Gibson came to their street |url=https://stlsportspage.com/2020/10/04/residents-on-a-street-in-st-louis-have-special-memories-of-the-day-bob-gibson-came-to-their-street/ |website=STLSPORTSPAGE |accessdate=2020-12-08 |date=2020-10-04 |archive-date=2021-05-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210524092923/https://stlsportspage.com/2020/10/04/residents-on-a-street-in-st-louis-have-special-memories-of-the-day-bob-gibson-came-to-their-street/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2014年1月，紅雀隊宣布吉布森和其他22名退休球員及員工被選為{{le|聖路易紅雀隊名人堂|St. Louis Cardinals Hall of Fame Museum}}成員，並參加{{le|2014年聖路易紅雀隊球季|2014 St. Louis Cardinals season|2014年}}首屆的頒獎典禮<ref>{{cite news |author=Cardinals Press Release |url=http://stlouis.cardinals.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20140118&content_id=66822534&vkey=pr_stl&c_id=stl |title=Cardinals establish Hall of Fame & detail induction process |website=Stlouis.cardinals |date=2014-01-18 |accessdate=2014-01-29 |archive-date=2014-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140126165854/http://stlouis.cardinals.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20140118&content_id=66822534&vkey=pr_stl&c_id=stl}}</ref>。直至逝世時，吉布森仍{{le|聖路易紅雀隊紀錄列表|List of St. Louis Cardinals team records#Pitching|紅雀隊上多項紀錄}}的保持人，包括251場勝投、先發482次、255場完投、56次完封、投球局數3,884.1局及3,117次三振<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.mlb.com/cardinals/fans/tribute/bob-gibson |title=存档副本 |access-date=2020-12-08 |archive-date=2021-05-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210524092914/https://www.mlb.com/cardinals/fans/tribute/bob-gibson |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

